---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Embed CalcTax Calculator on Your Website — Free Widget | CalcTax"
  description="Add a free Canadian income tax calculator to your website. Simple embed code, no signup required. Links back to CalcTax for full functionality."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 font-display tracking-tight">
        Embed the CalcTax Calculator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
        Add a free Canadian income tax calculator to your website or blog.
        Copy the embed code below — no signup, no API key, no cost.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose mb-10">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>
        The embed displays a simple tax lookup widget on your site. Visitors enter their
        salary and province, see an instant estimate, and can click through to CalcTax
        for the full calculator with RRSP, capital gains, and dividends.
      </p>

      <h2>Embed Code</h2>
      <p>Copy and paste this into your HTML:</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-5 mb-6 overflow-x-auto">
      <pre class="text-sm text-emerald-400 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>&lt;iframe
  src="https://calctax.ca/income-tax-calculator"
  width="100%"
  height="700"
  frameborder="0"
  style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px;"
  title="Canadian Income Tax Calculator 2025 — CalcTax"
&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;
  Powered by &lt;a href="https://calctax.ca" style="color: #0d9488;"&gt;CalcTax.ca&lt;/a&gt;
  — Free Canadian Tax Calculator
&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>

    <button
      type="button"
      id="copy-embed"
      class="bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-xl px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-teal-700 transition mb-10"
    >
      Copy Embed Code
    </button>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Embed Options</h2>
      <p>You can link directly to a specific province calculator:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>calctax.ca/ontario-income-tax-calculator</code> — Ontario</li>
        <li><code>calctax.ca/alberta-income-tax-calculator</code> — Alberta</li>
        <li><code>calctax.ca/bc-income-tax-calculator</code> — BC</li>
        <li><code>calctax.ca/quebec-income-tax-calculator</code> — Quebec</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Or use a specific calculator type:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>calctax.ca/rrsp-calculator</code> — RRSP Savings</li>
        <li><code>calctax.ca/self-employed-tax-calculator</code> — Self-Employed</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Guidelines</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>The embed is free for any website — personal blogs, business sites, news outlets</li>
        <li>Please keep the "Powered by CalcTax.ca" attribution visible</li>
        <li>The calculator stays up to date automatically — we update rates each tax year</li>
        <li>Questions? Contact us at <a href="/contact">hello@calctax.ca</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('copy-embed')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const code = `<iframe\n  src="https://calctax.ca/income-tax-calculator"\n  width="100%"\n  height="700"\n  frameborder="0"\n  style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px;"\n  title="Canadian Income Tax Calculator 2025 — CalcTax"\n></iframe>\n<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 8px;">\n  Powered by <a href="https://calctax.ca" style="color: #0d9488;">CalcTax.ca</a>\n  — Free Canadian Tax Calculator\n</p>`;
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(code);
      const btn = document.getElementById('copy-embed');
      if (btn) {
        btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
        setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = 'Copy Embed Code'; }, 2000);
      }
    });
  </script>
</Base>
